attributes.Long form description: The general instruction is to assemble the furniture. The student starts aligning the legs to the top table but the instructor tells him that he should start with the shelf instead. The student screws the first leg to the shelf and proceeds to do the same for the other three, he struggles sometimes inserting the hex socket heads into the holes. Then the student screws the top table to the legs and tighten all the hex socket heads.
